<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<!--<h4>First side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samastabhuvanāśraya
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śrīprithvīvallabha mahārā<unclear>jā</unclear>
<lb n="3"/>rāja paramēśvara paramabhaṭṭāraka <unclear>sa</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tyāśrayakuḷatiḷakaṁ cāḷukyā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>bharaṇaṁ śrīmatribhuvanamalladē
<lb n="6" break="no"/>varavijayarājyamuttarō
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ttarābhivriddhipravarddhamāna
<lb n="8" break="no"/>mācaṁdrārkkatāraṁbaraṁ
<lb n="9"/>kalyāṇada nelavīḍinalu sukasaṁ
<lb n="10" break="no"/><unclear>ka</unclear>thāvinōdadiṁ rājyaṁ geyu
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ttamire tatpādapadmōpajīvi 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="12" break="no"/>gaḷu svasti ca<unclear>raṇasarōruhavi</unclear>
<lb n="13" break="no"/>hātaviḷōcana triḷōcana pra<unclear>mu</unclear>
<lb n="14" break="no"/>khākhaḷa prithvēśvarakāritakāvērī
<lb n="15" break="no"/>tīra karikālakularatna pradēṣāhi
<lb n="16" break="no"/>takumārāṁkuśa śrīmanmahāma
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ṇḍaḷēśvaraṁ ghaṭiyaṁka kāṟa cō
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ḷamahārājaru śrīmaccāḷukya
<lb n="19" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> vikramagālada 49 neya raudri
<lb n="20" break="no"/>saṁvatsarada puṣya bahuḷa bidi
</p>

<p>[Rest of the inscription is lost].</p>

